title: 230. Q&AF: Difference Between Ego & Arrogance, Giving Friends Honest Feedback & Misconception About Failure
itunes:title: 230. Q&AF: Difference Between Ego & Arrogance, Giving Friends Honest Feedback & Misconception About Failure
description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on the difference between having an ego & being arrogant when operating at a high level, the best way to deliver honest criticism to a close friend, and what's the biggest misconception about failure.
